    "data": [
        {
            "title": "明尼蘇達州動盪難平 聯邦執法人員在該州又擊斃一人",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據新聞報導，周六美國聯邦<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:執法人員;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/執法人員\">執法人員</a>在明尼阿波利斯槍殺一名51 歲男子。目前該州正處於移民執法高壓狀態，全州多地出現動盪。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據美聯社和《Minneapolis Star-Tribune》報導，中槍男子在送醫後去世。官方未披露男子身份。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">明尼蘇達州州長蒂姆·沃爾茲宣布了這起槍擊事件，並在社交媒體上要求部署在該州的數千名聯邦執法人員立即撤離。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「今天早上聯邦執法人員再次製造了恐怖槍擊事件，我剛剛已與白宮進行了溝通，」沃爾茲在X上發貼稱，「明尼蘇達州已經受夠了。這件事令人作嘔。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a94d2df0-0505-395d-8454-e608243f9a45-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國土安全部的一名官員表示，槍擊受害者當時持有武器，但未提供更多細節。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據美聯社報導，槍擊發生後，旁觀者聚集在一起，對聯邦執法人員大聲辱罵，稱他們為「懦夫」並叫他們回家。在其他地點，執法人員還強行將一名大喊大叫的抗議者塞進車內。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國一女子在移民執法行動中被射殺 抗議民眾要求ICE「滾出去」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Federal Agents Shoot, Kill Person in Minnesota Amid Unrest</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Alicia A. Caldwell.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%98%8E%E5%B0%BC%E8%98%87%E9%81%94%E5%B7%9E%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%AA%E9%9B%A3%E5%B9%B3-%E8%81%AF%E9%82%A6%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%9C%A8%E8%A9%B2%E5%B7%9E%E5%8F%88%E6%93%8A%E6%96%83-%E4%BA%BA-171559678.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-25 02:46:03",
